# Cloudflare Pages redirects/rewrites for The Ballot Atlas.
#
# With Astro's base: '/ballot-atlas' config, internal links are
# prefixed with /ballot-atlas, but the build output puts static
# files at dist/ root. These rewrites strip the prefix on incoming
# requests so the right static file is served.
#
# Format: <from-path>  <to-path>  <status-code>
# Status 200 = silent rewrite (URL stays the same in the browser).
# Status 301 = permanent redirect (URL changes).
#
# Two rules are needed because /ballot-atlas/* requires at least
# one character after the slash, so the exact /ballot-atlas (map
# page root) needs its own rule.
#
# Path matters for Cloudflare Pages: this file lives in public/ so
# Astro copies it to dist/_redirects at build time, which is where
# Cloudflare Pages looks for it.

/ballot-atlas     /        200
/ballot-atlas/*   /:splat  200
